location.fullValue: Duval Plan, Arbors at Fair Oaks

data.description: A beautiful home in a gated neighborhood. A welcoming covered porch and double doors with wrought iron leading into the home. You are greeted with an open floor plan, high ceilings, neutral wall colors, crown molding and decorative floor tile. A gourmet style kitchen boasting granite, SS appliances, a gas cook-top with decorative backsplash and built-in double ovens. A center island houses a built-in microwave. The expansive breakfast bar is enhanced with stone and decorative post legs. An oversized walk-in pantry provides space for food and storage those small appliances. Gather in your living room with a gorgeous stone fireplace, flanked by built-in cabinetry. The spacious owner's retreat features wood laminate flooring and a spa-like bath with a walk-through shower and a separate tub. A generous size covered patio overlooks a large yard. Evening dining is elevated in a beautiful Gazebo next to a custom-designed water feature. This stunning home is on 0.48 acre lot with trees and has great potential. Solar panels, a side-entry three-car garage with an electric (EV) charging station. Conveniently located near I-10 with an abundance of dining and shopping.
